Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.93,0:00:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让它陷入了静寂而永恒的睡眠中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.60,0:00:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以那个森林即使是现在仍然遍布着坚硬的荆棘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.80,0:00:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断地阻止着来自外部的侵入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.95,0:00:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概 会持续到我死亡的时候为止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.09,0:02:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)}荆棘的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.08,0:02:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人她…？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.42,0:02:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.28,0:02:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考试结束后就是圣诞节呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.52,0:02:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄蔷薇大人说结业式时要在蔷薇馆开个联欢会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.79,0:02:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.92,0:02:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜欢圣诞节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.69,0:02:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要包装吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.27,0:02:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.38,0:02:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是流言中的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.03,0:02:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是放弃读这本书比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.59,0:02:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳怎么想呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.52,0:03:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我的话 会读的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一方面也有些在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.82,0:03:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先单纯地读读看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.01,0:03:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎样去读 如果白蔷薇大人的事真写在上面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.77,0:03:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.78,0:03:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须加星如果是白蔷薇大人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概我会更加尊敬她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.35,0:03:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会请她在文集上签名呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不错啊 你的这种性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.21,0:03:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 果然对是否读这本书犹豫不决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.34,0:03:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荆棘的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这本书的作者“须加星”实际上是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.16,0:03:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.99,0:03:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 那个白蔷薇大人出版了将自已\n隐藏的过去毫不隐瞒地拼缀起来的自白小说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.00,0:03:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种流言在到处流传
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说也只是流言而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.31,0:03:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些看过这本叫“大波斯菊通信”的\n新刊导读杂志上专题介绍的人们的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.76,0:04:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荆棘的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.20,0:04:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作者 须加星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.22,0:04:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学园里数月的生活是否只是梦幻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.38,0:04:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣将一切封印在了心中那荆棘的森林中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.08,0:04:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人期待的新人作家 冲击的自传性处女作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.75,0:04:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须加星与白蔷薇大人的真名“佐藤圣”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.23,0:04:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确“星”与“圣”发音相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.28,0:04:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且既然是自传性的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是将自已的过去写在了这本小说里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.40,0:04:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家会流言四起也是可以理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.89,0:04:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人过去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.37,0:04:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为一年级生的由乃你们大概不知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.68,0:04:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人的过去也可说是禁忌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都尽量不去提及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.88,0:04:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可说是一种“无言的理解”吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.04,0:04:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道事情的人大家都三缄其口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.03,0:04:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像在保护着什么似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.05,0:05:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是发生了什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.30,0:05:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.21,0:05:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我是一年级生 没有被告知详细的经过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.36,0:05:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去… 是去年的事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.92,0:05:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.04,0:05:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那个白蔷薇大人的过去写在了这本书里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.39,0:05:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人会犹豫也是不无道理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.96,0:05:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊 大人们想强制把互为挚友的圣与香织分开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.83,0:05:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是她们在圣诞夜里踏上了没有目的地的旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然她们两人想一起死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但当圣在病院里醒过来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.88,0:05:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香织已经去往天国了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.80,0:05:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很常见的结局嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.12,0:05:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学 你看到最后都没哭吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.63,0:05:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有些地方和我与祥子大人很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.56,0:05:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 想说的不是小说的内容啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确看了这个后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.68,0:06:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有流言说作者是白蔷薇大人倒也可以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.28,0:06:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小说的舞台只可能是莉莉安啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.50,0:06:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊 令虽然也看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.36,0:06:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就说“不要再插手这件事”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“就当没有读过这本小说”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.26,0:06:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“完全不想与流言有任何关联”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.51,0:06:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 祥子大人在买了文集后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉也是对读还是不读犹豫不决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.56,0:06:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令什么也不肯对我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.32,0:06:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 只有直接去问白蔷薇大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.94,0:06:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.07,0:06:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.11,0:06:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.71,0:06:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是只有去问白蔷薇大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.36,0:07:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 志摩子同学也一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.61,0:07:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.47,0:07:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…？ 你们不是姐妹吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.29,0:07:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不在意吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.40,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.14,0:07:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 佑巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.95,0:07:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在就去比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.27,0:07:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.20,0:07:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点的话 白蔷薇大人就会去蔷薇馆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.39,0:07:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在令大人与祥子大人面前问不出口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.99,0:07:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.00,0:07:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年级藤组 佐藤圣同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.44,0:07:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.27,0:07:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请立刻到生活指导室来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是因为那本小说？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.95,0:07:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 佑巳也被传唤了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.45,0:07:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.78,0:07:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.11,0:07:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是佑巳将我作为“搂抱魔”告发了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.47,0:08:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人 您还不知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.39,0:08:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.97,0:08:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我本来还想问您的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.34,0:08:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“荆棘的森林”的作者\n是否就是白蔷薇大人您或是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.84,0:08:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荆棘？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.93,0:08:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.14,0:08:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下去的话一会儿再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.66,0:08:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园长 中高等部校长 年级主任以及藤组的负责人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.37,0:08:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“荆棘的森林”已经变成这么严重的问题了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.16,0:08:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.69,0:08:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.26,0:08:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人怎么样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是跟往常一样开朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.56,0:08:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且好像还不知道被传唤的原因呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.55,0:08:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.13,0:08:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人会怎么样呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.55,0:08:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.77,0:08:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.53,0:09:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.84,0:09:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.65,0:09:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是值得告诉新闻部的东西 我们可是一点儿也不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.26,0:09:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说 帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.16,0:09:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人退学也无所谓吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.19,0:09:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退学！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.64,0:09:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的学园可是禁止打工的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.66,0:09:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写小说什么的明显是违反了校规啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.54,0:09:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退学什么的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.88,0:09:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果事情变成那样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用“莉莉安瓦版”来发起署名活动也无所谓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.34,0:09:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写上“请不要将白蔷薇大人退学”什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.79,0:09:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我们真的什么也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.71,0:09:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.41,0:09:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.82,0:09:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.95,0:09:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没法再支撑下去了 快站好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.68,0:09:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.26,0:09:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 在生活指导室里互相抱着摔在一起可不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.88,0:10:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉打扰到各位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.88,0:10:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.91,0:10:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到\n大家无法抑制的好奇心我还是先报告一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.07,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 写“荆棘的森林”的人不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.18,0:10:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 这一次不能向\n莉莉安瓦版提供新闻材料真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.29,0:10:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筑山三奈子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.91,0:10:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是蔷薇馆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.68,0:10:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概大家听到传唤的广播后都在等我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当华丽的传唤啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.74,0:10:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是从没有因个人的事情而被传唤过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.24,0:10:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有点羡慕你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.69,0:10:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是不敢当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是蔷薇大人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没像我这样慌里慌张的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了生活指导室吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.50,0:11:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.33,0:11:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.26,0:11:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.82,0:11:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.23,0:11:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上等品真是不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.84,0:11:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我先报告一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.03,0:11:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经向佑巳与由乃说过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.13,0:11:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流言中的那本小说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.47,0:11:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是被传唤的原因吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.56,0:11:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.38,0:11:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清楚地说明不是我写的之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.58,0:11:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园长为我说了好话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.63,0:11:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后简单地就让我离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.13,0:11:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自已既没有读过实物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.73,0:11:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且对于那个流传的谣言也是刚才才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.37,0:12:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不是你写的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.27,0:12:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向圣母玛莉亚发誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.54,0:12:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.05,0:12:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个话题就到此结束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.98,0:12:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？ 黄蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.66,0:12:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有异议 红蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.66,0:12:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.05,0:12:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 该讨论一下圣诞节的联欢会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.02,0:12:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.27,0:12:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都未受到流言的影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.04,0:12:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真是自我中心又浅薄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.75,0:12:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情低落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.15,0:12:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我脸上的表情又变来变去了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.83,0:12:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想发言吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.06,0:12:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.05,0:12:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.89,0:12:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要睡得迷迷糊糊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.06,0:12:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意见的人要好好地举起手来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟会为了这种人而烦恼真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.60,0:13:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.70,0:13:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手 白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.49,0:13:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 在闹情绪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.43,0:13:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子 把佑巳借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.26,0:13:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒是没什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.65,0:13:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.95,0:13:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会脱她的制服或是胡来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.27,0:13:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再开玩笑的话 我可要拒绝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.05,0:13:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令 把由乃也借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要由乃愿意的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.60,0:13:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.74,0:13:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么痛快就允诺没关系吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.04,0:13:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为令明白我不会对由乃淘气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那为什么只对我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为反应很有趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.03,0:13:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 祥子的反应也很让人开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.29,0:13:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是一次捉弄就会有双倍乐趣的姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.83,0:13:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.15,0:13:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.13,0:13:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.96,0:14:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我成了坏心前辈的饵食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.88,0:14:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 后面的收拾就由我们三人来做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.33,0:14:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家请先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.40,0:14:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么后面就拜讬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.23,0:14:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.63,0:14:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳 不要让白蔷薇大人太开心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.68,0:14:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.42,0:14:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 有需要我帮忙的事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.92,0:14:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在看起来也没什么需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.97,0:14:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们陪着姐姐真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.99,0:14:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.39,0:14:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让志摩子同学跟我们在一起不行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.25,0:14:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子是那种即使跟她说不要留下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.42,0:14:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要她想留下来就会凭自已的意志留下来的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.35,0:14:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在带着那本“荆棘的森林”吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.64,0:14:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.22,0:14:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能借我一下吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借倒是没什么问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.29,0:15:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您想做什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是读它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.82,0:15:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你以为我会拿它当锅垫吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.63,0:15:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么做为回礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.72,0:15:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面食堂的餐券？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.95,0:15:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来的时候在自动贩卖机那里帮我买一罐咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.49,0:15:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连你们的份也一起买好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.51,0:15:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人真是个不可预料的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.22,0:15:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子同学真是了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.96,0:15:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟能和那种人做姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.02,0:15:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 佑巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.64,0:15:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在颈上围上手帕比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.16,0:15:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣领会弄脏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.09,0:15:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.89,0:15:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.46,0:15:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人究竟是为了什么将我们留下来呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.79,0:15:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.99,0:15:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 如果只是为了借“荆棘的森林”的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.85,0:15:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接带回家去不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.92,0:15:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.31,0:16:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是因为我们太可爱 所以想要请我们吃拉面吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳同学 脑筋快成豆腐渣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.91,0:16:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.51,0:16:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.90,0:16:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般来说是不会买罐装年糕豆汤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.08,0:16:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.67,0:16:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.68,0:16:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？ 那个罐装年糕豆汤什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.69,0:16:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳同学买的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.10,0:16:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.67,0:16:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世界上还有这种东西存在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.05,0:16:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 白蔷薇大人要的咖啡我们可是好好地买来了哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.87,0:16:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.75,0:16:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经把书仔细地读完了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.75,0:16:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为“荆棘的森林”是我写的\N那些人也许真是有很好的直觉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.95,0:16:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.85,0:16:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不是跟我很像吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.14,0:16:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想问也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.41,0:17:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家会认为写那本小说的是我的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.95,0:17:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅是名字同音而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点你们也应该有些发觉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.74,0:17:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们毫不掩饰地流露出了那种好奇心吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.73,0:17:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是为了看你们这种表情才说这种话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.62,0:17:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想说的部份我不会说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.48,0:17:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也没问题的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.69,0:17:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.18,0:17:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为总觉得只有你们不知道不是很不公平吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.86,0:17:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了告诉我们才将我们留下来的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.70,0:17:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然也是为了想早点读到这本书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.06,0:17:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓉子与令她们之所以不向你们说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.88,0:17:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也许是为了体谅我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那么痛苦的事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.18,0:17:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾有过一个非常要好的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.32,0:17:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说她甚至比父母和兄弟更加重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.24,0:17:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢她到只要有她在 其它什么也不需要的地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.00,0:17:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个想着将来成为修女的纯洁的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.81,0:18:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 在去年的圣诞节里 她离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.05,0:18:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.47,0:18:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完完全全是“荆棘的森林”的圣与香织嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.59,0:18:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是完全相同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.35,0:18:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我既没有与那个朋友一起踏上旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.25,0:18:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有吞下安眠药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她转学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.57,0:18:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说香织还活着了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.07,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀 还活着很失望吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.45,0:18:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.58,0:18:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 难道是谁以白蔷薇大人\N的事作为参考而写下了这本小说吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.73,0:18:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既有不同的部份 也有相似得惊人的部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.83,0:18:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得生气吗 白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.72,0:18:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自已的过去被擅自写成了小说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还被人误认为是作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.80,0:18:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 只要能被最重要的人理解就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.28,0:19:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才想讲给你们俩听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.19,0:19:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我讨厌残留着误解与臆测的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.92,0:19:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转学的朋友 现在怎么样了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.38,0:19:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 怎么样了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.33,0:19:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想见她吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.86,0:19:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不见面 为好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.96,0:19:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人的名字 不是香织
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.49,0:19:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是久保 栞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.60,0:19:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人现在还喜欢着那个人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.92,0:19:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也这样想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.72,0:19:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才没有留下志摩子同学吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.86,0:19:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为会对志摩子同学很过意不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得不可原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.92,0:19:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明会有因小说而受到伤害的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.36,0:19:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.24,0:19:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写那本小说的不会是久保栞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.27,0:20:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.16,0:20:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.63,0:20:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会彻底查明写这本“荆棘的森林”的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.33,0:20:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是大波斯菊编辑部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.32,0:20:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要把我也拉来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令也很在意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“荆棘的森林”的作者到底是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.44,0:20:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.73,0:20:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉在忙碌的时候来打扰你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.24,0:20:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 你是“荆棘的森林”的负责人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.28,0:20:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是这样没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.09,0:20:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我不能将须加星的真实身份告诉你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.54,0:20:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.09,0:20:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这几天 来自莉莉安学生们的询问接连不断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.28,0:20:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“须加星的真实身份是否是佐藤圣”之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.50,0:20:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.12,0:20:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老…老师！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.53,0:20:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真令人怀念啊 这种制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.21,0:21:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到会在这种地方遇到后辈们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.63,0:21:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.88,0:21:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这么说您是莉莉安的毕业生了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.29,0:21:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是很久以前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.45,0:21:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.22,0:21:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.03,0:21:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是须加星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.41,0:21:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本名是春日诚子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.18,0:21:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么“荆棘的森林”的舞台果然是莉莉安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.72,0:21:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前发生的事情吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.63,0:21:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“荆棘的森林”是在如今\n连传闻都未留下的很久以前发生的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.07,0:21:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟白蔷薇大人的故事就像是其它的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.58,0:21:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没有从嘴里说出她的名字了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新生吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.24,0:21:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.04,0:22:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今年开始进入莉莉安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.58,0:22:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.83,0:23:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 花瓣的瓣是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.13,0:23:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个“瓣”啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.72,0:23:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老是拘泥在一些古怪的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.74,0:23:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花瓣的瓣写成汉字就是便当的“便”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.74,0:23:28.44,topfont,NTP,0,0,0,,注：日语中花瓣的“瓣”与便当的“便”同形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.46,0:23:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便当的“便”吗 原来如此 是便当的“便”啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.55,0:23:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周明明是个好故事 真觉得有点被糟塌啦
